snippet.title: Stray Souls - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to PC & consoles in 2023 - Wishlist Now on Steam: https://rebrand.ly/StraySoulsWishlist

Enter a world of nightmares in Stray Souls, a third person, action-horror game, inspired by the classics of the genre. Explore the sleepy town of Aspen Falls, as you fight terrifying creatures, solve mind-bending puzzles, and unravel a dark family secret to expose the chilling truth behind your existence.

NEVER MISS OUT ON NEWS!
SUBSCRIBE: https://bit.ly/2IPMij9 
FOLLOW US: https://allmylinks.com/StraySoulsGame
